guidanceOnLocatingIds:
Users can find identifiers by using this simple, searchable webpage - https://www.jerseyfsc.org/registry/documentsearch/

The identifier will be under the column header 'Number'
onlineAccessDetails: Data available through simple search engine, or documents can be downloaded at request for a fee
description: Companies in Jersey register with the Jersey Companies Registry. This information is maintained in a database and can be searched by users for free, and bulk data and more detailed documents can be accessed for a fee
name: Jersey Companies Registry
